n from the Israelites’ fellowship sacrifices. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They are to bring the thigh of the contribution and the breast of the presentation offering, together with the food offerings of the fat portions, to present as a presentation offering before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". It will belong permanently "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:28","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 30:21","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:18","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:22","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":22,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 24:9","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 18:8","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":8,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 18:11","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":11,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 18:19","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":19,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:22","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" to you and your children, as the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" commanded.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:28","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":28},{"label":"Ex 30:21","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":21},{"label":"Lv 6:18","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":18},{"label":"Lv 6:22","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":22},{"label":"Lv 24:9","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":9},{"label":"Nm 18:8","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 18:11","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":11},{"label":"Nm 18:19","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 5:22","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Moses inquired carefully about the male goat of the sin offering, but it had already been burned up. He was angry with Eleazar and Ithamar, Aaron’s surviving sons, and asked, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Why didn’t you eat the sin offering in the sanctuary area? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:26","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:29","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" For it is especially holy, and he has assigned it to you to take away the guilt "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 5:31","book":"Num","chapter":5,"verse":31,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the community "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 28:38","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":38,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 14:2","book":"Hos","chapter":14,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:29","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":29,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and make atonement for them before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 6:26","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":26},{"label":"Lv 6:29","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":29},{"label":"Nm 5:31","book":"Num","chapter":5,"verse":31},{"label":"Ex 28:38","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":38},{"label":"Hs 14:2","book":"Hos","chapter":14,"verse":2},{"label":"Jn 1:29","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Since its blood was not brought inside the sanctuary, you should have eaten it in the sanctuary area, as I commanded.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:26","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 6:29","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":29,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 6:26","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":26},{"label":"Lv 6:29","book":"Lev","chapter":6,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Aaron replied to Moses, “See, today they presented their sin offering and their burnt offering before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". Since these things have happened to me, if I had eaten the sin offering today, would it have been acceptable in the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s sight?” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:10:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When Moses heard this, it was acceptable to him. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit acceptable in his sight"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit acceptable in his sight"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099242526}